            <p class="about-text">The main purpose of this site is to help Playstation players get achievements trophy from their games. The name of the site was inspired by the Platinum Trophy, the highest achievement trophy(which means that the player has earned all of the game's achievements) on the playstation , hence the name Platinum Collector. The site displays all of the game's achievements. Each achievement has a comment form underneath for anyone to write their own tips or tricks to help other players get the achievement faster. In addition, there is a bookmarking feature so that users can quickly find the information they are looking for the next time they visit the site.</p>
